a good portion of the Huo Army.

23
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:49,280
I can send my troops to back you up.

24
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,680
What do you want in return?

25
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,240
I want

26
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,520
the Huo family to fall.

27
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:02,240
I want the Sheng family to gain

28
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,800
military power too.

29
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,919
With me on your side,

30
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,680
your odds will improve a lot.

31
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:13,240
This benefits both

32
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,479
you and me.

33
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:16,000
Deal.

34
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:24,159
Well then, here's to a successful partnership.

35
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,520
These belong to Feifei, right?

36
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:34,400
I'll take care of them for her.

37
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,120
