These belong to you, right?

42
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:07,439
They were at Sheng Weilian's place.

43
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,639
These should be Liu Yiyi's.

44
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,080
They often met there in secret.

45
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,800
When I was a child,

46
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,800
I played with knives.

47
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,879
I never played with dolls.

48
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,839
We've grown up surrounded by hatred.

49
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,680
Marry me once all of this

50
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,879
is over.

51
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,680
We'll leave Sucheng to start a new life.

52
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,560
We'll buy a small house together.

53
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:01,319
Work at sunrise, rest at sunset.

54
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,680
Three simple meals a day,

55
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,759
plain and humble.

56
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,800
Living the simplest life.

57
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,399
Then, we'll have children

58
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,319
and grow old together.

