of the Huo Army.

110
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,720
The Huo Army?

111
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,279
This was once the Gu family.

112
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:31,039
Your Huo Army used to be the Gu Army!

113
00:10:37,190 --> 00:10:37,799
